<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>السَّيْر/ع، المَشْي/ع،<span class="c5"> الجَرْي:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَسِيرُ شَأْوَاً وَأَرْكَبُ شَأْوَاً،<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> أَسِيرُ شَوْطَاً وَأَرْكَبُ شَوْطَاً<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الشِّجَار/ع، المُشَاجَرَة/ع، العِرَاك/ع،<span class="c5"> المَعْرَكَة/ع:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الحِجِّيزَى:</span> التَّحْجِيزُ وَالمحَاجَزَة ٠<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الصَّبيّ:</span> <span class="c4">[انْظُرِ الرَّجُلَ ٠ بحَرْفِ الرَّاء]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الصُّلْح:</span> <span class="c4">[انْظُرِ الحُبَّ بِحَرْفِ الحَاء]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">بَابُ الصِّفَات/ع:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">الجَحْدَر:</span> الرَّجُلُ الجَعْدُ القَصِير، وَالأُنْثَى جَحْدَرَة،<span class="c5"> وَيُقَال:</span> جَحْدَرَ صَاحِبَهُ وجَحْدَلَهُ: إَذَا صَرَعَهُ ٠ <span class="c3">{لِسَانُ العَرَب: ٤/ ١١٨}</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
